trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: "戻る"または"進む"ナビゲーション履歴にエントリを表します。

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]1 つのエントリがされて以前に移動、ナビゲーション履歴と同じようにコンテンツの各部分を格納するナビゲーション履歴サービスを実装する[!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)]です。

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: ナビゲーション履歴には、1 つ"戻る"ナビゲーション履歴を記憶を使用し、次に進むナビゲーション履歴を記憶する&1; つを使用する、2 つのスタックが構成されます。

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: 現在のアイテムのエントリは、前方のナビゲーションが発生したときに、ナビゲーション履歴をバックアップするが追加されます。

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: これは、次の状況で発生します -`Navigate`メソッドが呼び出されます (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>)。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 。

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: -`GoForward`メソッドが呼び出されます (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: ナビゲーションの転送ボタン[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]現在のナビゲーターからに表示される ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: 同様に、現在のアイテムのエントリが追加"進む"ナビゲーション履歴を戻るナビゲーションが発生すると、動作は、前に場合: -`GoBack`メソッドが呼び出されます (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: [戻る] ボタンでナビゲーション[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]現在のナビゲーターからに表示される ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: 各エントリに戻ると"進む"ナビゲーション履歴は、JournalEntry クラスのインスタンスです。

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: 各 JournalEntry オブジェクトのエントリの名前を含む特定のナビゲーションに関する情報をカプセル化 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>) エントリを保持するかどうか、(<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) および[!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)]コンテンツへの移動がへの (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: 戻るナビゲーション履歴内のすべての JournalEntry オブジェクトを取得するには、列挙、<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>または<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>プロパティ</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: "進む"ナビゲーション履歴 JournalEntry のすべてのオブジェクトを列挙することによって取得できます、<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>または<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>プロパティ</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: ナビゲーション履歴から最新の JournalEntry オブジェクトを削除する必要がある場合、ナビゲーションを防ぐためになどを呼び出すことができます、`RemoveBackEntry`メソッド (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>)、JournalEntry オブジェクトを削除し、それへの参照を返しますこれ</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntry オブジェクトに追加できませんナビゲーション履歴、ただし、ためインスタンス化も、JournalEntry から派生することができに、そのためにはメンバーを実装する型がないためです。

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: ただし、呼び出すことによってナビゲーション履歴のバックアップを作成するカスタムの<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>オブジェクトを追加することができます、`AddBackEntry`メソッド (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>、 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>、 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>) です。<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>を追加、<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>を内部的に作成された JournalEntry オブジェクトには、"戻る"ナビゲーション履歴に追加するオブジェクト</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService></xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>。
